Title: Worcester Greenstar Oilfit plume management kit
Description: This Worcester Greenstar Oilfit plume management kit is suitable for oil boiler use. Plume management kits are used to solve the issue of nuisance pluming, where the plume from a condensing boiler causes an obstruction in a garden, side passage or courtyard. The kit simply redirects the plume away from the property to a more convenient location.
